\N<Yu-kun>Hey, Boku-kun. Do you want to play
together?
\N<Boku>Yeah, let's play! What do you want to do?

\N<Yu-kun>Hmm, yeah... Since we have a spacious
place, how about flying paper airplanes?

\N<Yu-kun>Oh, I see. In that case, let's compete
to see who can fly them the farthest.

\N<Yu-kun>Well then, shall we have a paper
airplane competition today too?

\N<Boku>Yeah!... Oh... My paper airplane flew
away...
\N<Yu-kun>Shall we go and get it together?
\N<Boku>No, it's okay! I'll go get it later!

\N<Girl>Hehe. Hey, Boku-kun. Can you guess who I
am?

\N<Boku>Huh? I wonder who it could be...? We
haven't met before, right...? Hmm... Ah!

\N<Boku>Could it be, you're Yuko-chan's Onee-
chan, right? I think I heard that she has an older
sister before!

\N<Girl>Huh...? Ah, y-yes, that's right. I'm
Yuko's older sister... Yuko-chan. Nice to meet
you, Boku-kun.

\N<Boku>Yeah! Nice to meet you, Yuko-chan! So,
where is Yuko-kun today?

\N<Yuko-chan>Ah, um, Yuu has something to do today
and couldn't come.

\N<Boku>I see. Well then, how about we play
together with Yuko-chan today?

\N<Boku>Well then, what should we play? I wonder
what girls usually play. Hey, Yuko-chan, what kind
of games do you usually play?

\N<Yuko-chan>U-um... w-well... how about...? Oh, I
know, why don't we go to your house, Boku-kun?

\N<Boku>My house? Yeah, that's fine! Alright,
let's go, Yuko-chan!

\N<Yu-kun>Ah, Boku-kun. What do you want to do
today?
エッチなこと、したいな
エッチなこと、したいな

\N<Yu-kun>Hehe, is that so? ♥ Sure, let's go to
your room, Boku-kun ♥

\N<Yu-kun>Shall we have another paper airplane
competition today?

\N<Boku>Yeah!... Ah... My paper airplane flew away
and hasn't come back...
\N<Yu-kun>Shall we go together to retrieve it?
\N<Boku>No, it's okay! I'll go get it later!
